ober to december  and as chief operating officer from february  to january  mr waddell served as a board member of northern trust from february  to november  prior to becoming the chairman of the board key contributions to the board as chairman and chief executive officer of northern trust corporation and the northern trust company mr waddell possesses broad financial services experience with a strong record of leadership in a highly regulated industry source abbvie on    sign up for equilar atlas and view frederick h waddells full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like frederick h waddell more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in frederick h waddells network and community follow changes in frederick h waddells employment and moneyinmotion connect with frederick h waddell through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example frederick h waddell frederick h waddells connections  sign up now to view frederick h waddells  connections » brian t moynihan president chief executive officer and chairman of the board bank of america corporation roxanne s austin board member abbott laboratories edward b rust board member sp global inc kessel d stelling chairman of the board chief executive officer and president synovus financial corp jose l prado board member northern trust corporation david h smith board member illinois tool works inc charles a tribbett board member northern trust corporation michael h moskow board member discover financial services william a osborn board member caterpillar inc martin p slark board member hub group inc popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla jan koum board member facebook inc philip l milstein board member the marcus corporation × claim your pr